thermo_style custom step etotal enthalpy pe ke temp press vol density cella cellb cellc cellalpha cellbeta cellgamma f_freeze2[1] f_freeze2[2] f_freeze2[3] v_Pz0 v_Fric v_layFric1 v_layFric2 v_layFric3 v_layFric4 v_layFric5 v_layFric6 v_layFric7 v_layFric8 v_layFric9 v_layFric10 v_layFric11 v_layFric12 v_layFric13 v_layFric14 v_layFric15 v_layFric16 v_layFric17 v_layFric18
